[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[2m  No saved GitHub Copilot credentials (current: Azure AI Foundry). Let's configure them.\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[2m\u001b[22m\r\n"]
