[0.000, "o", "\u001b[36m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[36m  Copilot uses a one-time browser login (device-code OAuth) — your `gh` PAT can't be reused\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m  because the standard `gh auth login` scope doesn't include the Copilot integration.\u001b[22m\r\n\u001b[2m\u001b[22m\r\n"]
